        <h1>About Song Tracker</h1>
        <p>Song Tracker is an application designed to keep track of songs you want to learn and play on your musical instruments.</p>

        <h2>Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Track songs you want to play next</li>
            <li>Create and manage your profile</li>
            <li>Search for artists and songs</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>Register for an account, and start adding songs to your profile. You can organize your music for practice and never forget which songs you wanted to learn.</p>
        
        <h2>Get Started</h2>
        <p><a href="/Register">Register</a> for an account or <a href="/Login">log in</a> if you already have one.</p>
